{"tid":992833,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"自動沖水系統 我屌你老母呀！","createTime":"2019-01-23T12:52:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-23T14:05:35.000Z","uid":220416,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3451ca66c8b1ac12b432a5ba8abc9f81d71804ad","tid":992833,"uid":220416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T12:52:49.000Z","msg":"事源係咁 小弟搭地鐵人有三急<br />\n咁啱經過旺角 咪落車去廁所解決囉<br />\n一除褲坐低 屌你個老母佢沖水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲水花彈撚到我成個屎窟都係<br />\n搞到我好似個90歲廢老咁<br />\n全程烏低個身痾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔係話自動沖水系統有咩問題<br />\n但係可唔可以唔好整係背脊位度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n爆一次石沖五六次水<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ve6n0kp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVe6n0kp.png&h=071577ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"69325491a1246b1853742b207845833bd6ddca5f","tid":992833,"uid":810,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T12:53:50.000Z","msg":"有圖係好 但張圖有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f52ed63176d6e0b003e95f3f2b23c4be9f2e6e0","tid":992833,"uid":90820,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"69325491a1246b1853742b207845833bd6ddca5f","tid":992833,"uid":810,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T12:53:50.000Z","msg":"有圖係好 但張圖有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T12:55:12.000Z","msg":"顯示個sensor位置有幾咁濕鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p